{"tid":1174962,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有陣時真係想返屋企做個廢青算","createTime":"2019-05-28T08:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T16:26:34.000Z","uid":229095,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4a113859e48abf52814b11ce836f899a7c09bf8d","tid":1174962,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"grad左一年<br />\n日日返工都唔知返工有咩意思<br />\n做d完全冇興趣冇意義嘅野<br />\n好似生命就係為左人地而活咁<br />\n每個月返工都只係夠比家用同日常開支<br />\n慶幸嘅係每個月都可以買下少少自己野<br />\n有時真係唔知自己想點<br />\n係香港生活真係好辛苦<br />\n點解我唔可以抽到支上上籤做鬼佬<br />\n做個waiter都可以渣車返工<br />\n我就要係香港逼地鐵<br />\n屌你老母臭閪<br />\n遲早搞到自己有反社會人格"},{"pid":"ec8d512c9efca5583bf8b367670b14184ef61d28","tid":1174962,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"香港係生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76971f87b2c586fa75497db51170333ad16c45a4","tid":1174962,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:23:28.000Z","msg":"生存 not 生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0785697db015fabdb7e0c1a8f2ecb8985e9fe6","tid":1174962,"uid":232491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"Can&rsquo;t agree more<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日過咁嘅生活 都麻木左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1441524a9e39f57eba46bc2710ab4c1f8774633e","tid":1174962,"uid":239565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:42:45.000Z","msg":"草錢買車啦"},{"pid":"71f7198664c7b29869dfdbeb3660ca7d473eaf9a","tid":1174962,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"你哩啲問題你班讀唔成書嘅同學幾年前已經諗過，到你宜家出嚟做嘢嘅時候可能佢地已經揸緊車返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9e73c1efc13d860681e45e2f825e1ba54007b